name: 'Blackened' Horween Front Pocket Wallet
description:
We were missing a full on black wallet so here you go. 
A soft Horween tanned full grain leather front pocket wallet. Built to carry only your bare essentials: 10 - 12 cards + some cash. This leather has a matte black finish with black stitching.

American made.
Lifetime warranty.
Handstitched.
2 stitch size choices: Biggy or Smalls.
Stitch size in image is: Smalls.
